spec_data.Name: geany-plugins-geanyinsertnum
spec_data.Description:
Geanyinsertnum replaces a (possibly zero-width) rectangular selection with
integer numbers, using start/step/base etc. specified by the user. For
practical reasons, the number of lines is limited to 500000.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 09:26:53 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Insert huge number ranges with small efforts
